{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 62,
  "title": "第六十二章（道注）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "道者 萬物之注也 善人之寳也 不善人之所寳也"
    },
    {
      "text": "美言可以市 尊行可以賀人 人之不善 何棄之有"
    },
    {
      "text": "故立天子 置三卿 雖有拱之璧以先四馬 不善坐 而進此"
    },
    {
      "text": "古之所以貴此者何也 不謂求以得 有罪以免輿 故為天下貴"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "奧，藏也。道為萬物之藏，無所不容也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善人以道為身寶，不敢違也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道者，不善人之保倚也。遭患逢急，猶自知悔卑下。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 1
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "美言者獨可於市耳。夫市交易而退，不相宜善言美語，求者欲疾得，賣者欲疾售也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "加，別也。人有尊貴之行，可以別異於凡人，未足以尊道。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 13,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人雖不善，當以道化之。蓋三皇之前，無有棄民，德化淳也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "欲使教化不善之人。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "雖有美璧先駟馬而至，故不如坐進此道。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "古之所以貴此道者，不日日遠行求索，近得之於身。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "有罪謂遭亂世，闇君妄行形誅，修道則可以解死，免於眾也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 22,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道德洞遠，無不覆濟，全身治國，恬然無為，故可為天下貴也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "奧，猶曖也。可得庇蔭之辭。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "寶以為用也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "保以全也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言道無所不先，物無有貴於此也。雖有珍寶璧馬，無以匹之，美言之則可以奪眾貨之賈，故曰，美言可以市也，尊行之則千里之外應之，故曰，可以加於人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 13,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不善當保道以免放。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言以尊行道也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此道，上之所云也。言故立天子、置三公，尊其位、重其人，所以為道也。物無有貴於此者。故雖有拱抱寶璧以先，駟馬而進之，不如坐而進此道也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以求則得求，以免則得免，無所而不施，故為天下貴也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
